"And
Sauniere
was
knowledgeable
about
this?"
"Nobody
more
so."
"I
see."
Langdon
sensed
Fache
did
not
see
at
all.
Jacques
Sauniere
was
considered
the
premiere
goddess
iconographer
on
earth.
Not
only
did
Sauniere
have
a
personal
passion
for
