Wicca,
and
the
sacred
feminine,
but
during
his
twenty
year
tenure
as
curator,
Sauniere
had
helped
the
Louvre
amass
the
largest
collection
of
goddess
art
on
earth
labrys
axes
from
the
priestesses'
oldest
Greek
shrine
in
Delphi,
gold
